This is a Spring Boot Project for my Final Exam
This uses Spring Web for MVC, Thymeleaf for Templating Views.
It will demonstrate the use of RestTemplate to consume API from AirLabs and display the result to a webpage.

How to Build and Run:
1. First clone this repository to your local computer
2. Within the project directory open a Command Line Runner or Command Prompt
    (Note if you're using VS Code you can use the Terminal instead)
3. Build the dockerfile using the following command:
"docker build -t airline-app ."

4. After build completes run the docker image using the following command:
"docker run -p 8080:8080 -e API_KEY=<Your API KEY from AirLabs> airline-app

5. Open your browser and go to "http://localhost:8080"
